      <p><strong><a href="http://blog.nus.edu.sg/cdtkdr/2013/03/08/flipped-classes/" target="new">The Slow Road To Flipping </a><em><strong><br />
      </strong>Technology in Pedagogy, </em>no. 14, February   2013<br />
      <strong>By Ashish   Lall</strong> &amp;<strong> Laksh Samavedham</strong><em><br />
              </em></strong>There has been a lot of buzz and interest in the flipped classroom approach to teaching. This article shares the experiences of moving from a lecture based approach to a blended or flipped classroom. 
